andysofun 2025-04-04 04:05 p.m.
Your honor, I move for an acquittal (directed verdict) on the basis that the government hasn't proven their charges beyond a reasonable doubt.
1. The government has failed to introduce any testimony to establish that my client fired his weapon at Matrix_oc or that my client even had a weapon.
